item.title: Mechanics of Rubiks Cube #PID1.1
item.description: The Rubik’s Cube is a 3D combination puzzle that has fascinated minds for decades. Invented in 1974 by Ernő Rubik, a Hungarian architect and professor, it was originally called the “Magic Cube.
